<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5446370">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5446370/" class="title-link">达尔的代表作之一，一部关于现代政治分析的奠基...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5446370"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/42744542/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u42744542-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/42744542/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">政治学博士</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-05-29"
      class="main-meta">2012-05-29 16:32:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5446370_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在一般人的眼中，社会科学方面的著作有这样共同的特点：假话多、大话多、空话多。所以人们得出的普遍结论是：看不看社会科学方面的书籍一个样，要不要社会科学家一个样。说实话，曾几何时，我也有此种想法。 　　 可是，在我无意中读过美国当代著名政治学家罗伯特·Ａ·达尔所...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5446370/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">13有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中国人民大学出版社2012版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5446370_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5446370_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1215193">
        

